  "text": "As indicated above, the Excellence Study was the first one to compare the perceptions of communication professionals with those of top executives [CITATION_1] . Based on an interdisciplinary literature review, a quantitative survey was conducted among 327 organizations in the United States, Canada and Great Britain including 168 companies (Grunig et al., 2002, p. 3).",
